title: Hawaiian Explorer.rar
description: Hawaiian Explorer: Pearl Harbor is an addicting treasure hunt game where you will scour caves, beaches, shops, and shipwrecks in search for the legendary 800 year old Japanese Diamond Medal. You will be part of an extreme search and find team working for an eccentric multi-millionaire who has a passion for traveling and world treasures. With 15 fun and challenging missions and 4 bonus games, this game will keep you entertained for hours on end.
